			<h2>Why apparel design matters</h2>
			<p>Brands create apparel for their audience to give them clothing that not only appeals to their aesthetic preferences, but also conveys the brand’s values and message. Apparel is a powerful form of communication and brands use it to make a statement about who they are and what they stand for. Clothing can be used to attract new customers and build loyalty with existing ones, while helping to build an emotional connection with their target audience.</p>
